title: 1942 - The Men of the Golden West (Comedy) American Western film starring Roy Rogers

sources.title: 1942 - The Men of the Golden West (Comedy) American Western film starring Roy Rogers
sources.description:
The Brightest Star In The Western Sky... Blazing Across The Screen In His Most Sensational Motion Picture!
Lambert owns the trucking line that ships cattle to market. When he raises his rates Roy decides to ship the cattle on the River Boat. When Lambert and his men are unable to stop the boat, they rustle the cattle.

Main cast:
Roy Rogers - Roy
Smiley Burnette - Frog
Ruth Terry - Mary Lou Popen
Walter Catlett - Col. Silas Popen
Edmund MacDonald - Ross Lambert
George "Gabby" Hayes - Gabby
Bob Nolan - Bob (leader of the Sons of the Pioneers)

Directed by Joseph Kane
